In order to build on various platforms, the following CFLAGS should be used:

(NOTE: we should probably integrate this into configure.in)

AIX
---

CFLAGS="-DOLD_IPV6=1"

SOLARIS 8
---------

CFLAGS="-DSOLARIS2=8 -DOLD_IPV6=1"

SOLARIS 9
---------
 
CFLAGS="-DSOLARIS2=9 -DOLD_IPV6=1"

SOLARIS 10
----------

CFLAGS="-DSOLARIS2=10 -DHAVE_NETINET_IP_COMPAT_H=1"
